content: Most fans stayed at the gig on Copacabana Beach. You can simply enjoy the beach the day after and go home whenever you want. That's what Brazilians do when celebrating New Year's: they stay at the beach, having fun, drinks, and enjoying themselves until morning. Some even stay longer. You can just call an uber and go home after. there are millions of ubers and taxis.
